➜【星连文学社】宽哥：  《桂殿秋》
http://www.sohu.com/a/413686084_100115135	23255
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/3be5003a91a646b6b29cb063b1819cc0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> <strong>《桂殿秋》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 文/宽哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">金风细，桂花香。颐府紫气笼高堂。轻摇醁醑频频劝，把盏新茶细细尝。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">佳客闹，主人忙。小儿趣语笑逐狂。银笙丽影兴难尽，醉眼酣然上玉床。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200818/1f0e8130ef3f4e3eaae256bfdf376e48.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200818/e465ba2bde5a4d3e9b2a104178f87445.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
