➜【星连文学社】苏坛：《大理》
http://www.sohu.com/a/413688329_100115135	23960
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/37129ecdefe54654a201da3fad0ffa46.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《大理》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/苏坛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想追寻夕阳中的最后一抹余晖</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是谁？丹青妙手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">绘就一幅金色晚霞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">捋一丝惆怅于天边</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>心曲依旧是高山流水</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>苍山洱海间</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>把风花雪月唱和在</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>蝴蝶泉边</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">崇圣寺三塔依旧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古城中流过多少爱恨情仇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只是江山千年不变</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">载不动片片飞舞的落雪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200818/50ac88c9c0c14229b56a3e0a09604176.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
