<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/911ab4c4e02948bbb6e609e166ca9328.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>独自在天边燃成绿色火把(题画)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/朱翠荣(武汉)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如梦似幻，唯美一幅画</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是情有爱还恨？天空乌黑氤氲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">若我是那一棵树</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一定挣脱心绪束缚，不再理乱麻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">任它雷鸣电扯</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来吧，像我一样伫立草原</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>耕风沐雨根藏深邃</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>伸直伸展刺向青天，孑然何妨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>枝叶闪电繁茂在暴雨后</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>放出绿色火把</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我的火炬把原野燃成春</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不用借词虚拟美惹人眷念</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">阳光映碧羊群草中撒欢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一棵大树天边，若你置身此烟云意境</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">定会坠入诗意。一生太短</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来个打马畅快，明丽在辽阔绿原</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
